<div class="NavHead" style="font-size: 105%; background: transparent; text-align: left; background:#FFC569;;">Scripture classification</div>
<div class="NavContent" style="font-size: 105%; padding: 0.2em 0 0.4em; text-align: center; padding-bottom:1.0em;;"><a href="%C5%9Aruti" title="Śruti">Śruti</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span> <a href="Smriti" title="Smriti">Smriti</a></div>
