<div class="NavHead" style="font-size: 105%; background: transparent; text-align: left; background:#FFC569;;">Timeline</div>
<div class="NavContent" style="font-size: 105%; padding: 0.2em 0 0.4em; text-align: center; padding-bottom:1.0em;;"><a href="Timeline_of_Hindu_texts" title="Timeline of Hindu texts">Hindu texts</a></div>
