<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Hindu_texts&action=edit&section=10.php.html" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="References">References</span></h2>
<div class="reflist" style="list-style-type: decimal;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-1"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">see e.g. <a href="#CITEREFMacDonell2004">MacDonell 2004</a>, pp.&#160;29–39; <i>Sanskrit literature</i> (2003) in Philip's Encyclopedia. Accessed 2007-08-09</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-2"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">see e.g. <a href="#CITEREFRadhakrishnanMoore1957">Radhakrishnan &amp; Moore 1957</a>, p.&#160;3; Witzel, Michael, "Vedas and <span title="International Alphabet of Sanskrit Transliteration" class="Unicode" style="white-space:normal; text-decoration: none">Upaniṣads</span>", in: <a href="#CITEREFFlood2003">Flood 2003</a>, p.&#160;68</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-3"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Apte, pp. 109f. has "not of the authorship of man, of divine origin"</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-4"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFApte1965">Apte 1965</a>, p.&#160;887</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFMuller1891">Muller 1891</a>, pp.&#160;17–18</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFFlood1996">Flood 1996</a>, p.&#160;82</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Swami Nikhilananda, <i>The Upanishads: A New Translation</i> Vol.I, at 3-4 (5th Ed. 1990) <a href="Special_BookSources/0911206159" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-911206-15-9</a></span></li>
