<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Hindu_texts&action=edit&section=11.php.html" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Further_reading">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Kapoor, Dr. S.S. (2005). <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=a9EqbEi11FoC">Hinduism: An Introduction (History, Scriptures, Prayers and Phylosophy)</a>.</i></li>
</ul>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Hindu_texts&action=edit&section=12.php.html" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.sacred-texts.com/hin/index.htm">Sacred-Texts: Hinduism</a></li>
